Subject: Unable to add user to console
Description:
hello support,

I am unable to add new user to the console.  I added her in the Access as an admin but it is still showing as failed.
Solution_Comment__c:
For future reference: "To enable Role Based Access within Enterprise Auditor, corresponding roles must first be created within SQL Management Studio. Then Enterprise Auditor users must be assigned roles both in SQL Management Studio and in Enterprise Auditor."

https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Admin/Settings/Access/RoleBased/ConfigureRoles.htm
